						               													<description>Malevaje is a game for 1 to 4 players, where brave Malevos from the &amp;quot;hundred neighborhoods of Buenos Aires&amp;quot; face each other for prestige. Simple mechanics of fights through a Duel Deck from which the players will choose the Attack, Team or Action cards to use or discard, making the most of it. Fights full of adrenaline where with a lot of cunning and a little luck you will lead your Malevos to be the most respected and powerful.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the game, you will confront your fighter against the opponent. Each fighter has strong and weak defense in 3 parts of the body (head, body and lower parts), health (measured in feathers) and a reputation that the player offers in the fight to the player who wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player will also receive 5 &amp;quot;clever&amp;quot; tokens that can be used to avoid some of the cards during the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All players play on the same deck that has different attacks, actions and equipment. Then, during his turn, while drawing cards, will decide if to play an attack card, an action card or take equipment.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game will be defined into rounds (those depend on the number of players) and will the one that wins the most &amp;quot;respect&amp;quot; summing up the rounds.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
